# サプライチェーン攻撃対策: npm/pnpmの公開後24時間(1440分)未満のパッケージを除外
if (Test-Path "{{ .chezmoi.homeDir }}/.npmrc") {
    $content = Get-Content "{{ .chezmoi.homeDir }}/.npmrc" -Raw
    if ($content -match '(?m)^minimum-release-age=') {
        $content = $content -replace '(?m)^minimum-release-age=.*', 'minimum-release-age=1440'
        Set-Content "{{ .chezmoi.homeDir }}/.npmrc" $content -NoNewline
    } else {
        Add-Content "{{ .chezmoi.homeDir }}/.npmrc" 'minimum-release-age=1440'
    }
} else {
    Set-Content "{{ .chezmoi.homeDir }}/.npmrc" 'minimum-release-age=1440'
}
